title: BigFish Games - Mystery Case Files Return to Ravenhearst - New H
description:
Mystery Case Files Return to Ravenhearst

Constructed in 1895, Ravenhearst Manor stood as a symbol of 
affection from Charles Dalimar toward his love, 
Emma Ravenhearst. A month after the home was completed, 
its namesake went missing. Decades passed and 

the history of the home became a distant memory until one day, 
Emma&#039;s diary resurfaced.
In Mystery Case Files: Ravenhearst, players reassembled 
the diary and brought closure to this horrible tale. 
Or so they thought...

Thanx to TAC-CM
